Package org.whiteflag.protocol.core Description

Whiteflag Protocol Core Java Library

This package provides a library that defines Whiteflag core protocol features as specified in the Whiteflag standard in Java. As such, it is not a fully functional implementation of the protocol. This is to seperate core protocol features from implementation-specific design decisions.
